---
title: Parmesan Pan-Fried Shrimp and Gnocchi with Spinach and Peas
description: Golden, pan-fried gnocchi add a delicious twist to classic Alfredo! Rich cream, savoury Parmesan and succulent shrimp come together to make a luscious sauce.
